data.actual_result: All sorts of random users are on the list.
data.expected_result: Only the users that has the permission to make changes that gets recorded in audit log, gets listed in "Filter by User", like the desktop version.
data.short_description: On audit log, "Filter by User" gives you bunch of people who doesn't have the permission to make changes that gets logged in Audit log.
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to audit logs, and select on Filter by User. - Observe the names of the users listed.
